abstract: Great offenses tend to be greater than great defenses. Advantage, New England.
snippet: Great offenses tend to be greater than great defenses. Advantage, New England.
lead_paragraph: This Sunday features an A.F.C. East showdown when the Jets travel to Foxborough to take on the Patriots. I looked at my write-up for this same matchup from Week 13 last season, and much of what I wrote a year ago could be cut and pasted for this week, complete with the unstoppable force-immovable object cliché.

headline.main: Week 5 N.F.L. Game Probabilities, Including Jets-Patriots
